{"tid":2478571,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"2人被控營救理大期間危險駕駛 控方今申請撤銷擔保","createTime":"2021-04-07T07:10:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T07:51:58.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3e3959f18aad3196450b4014ef171aba32c5ed28","tid":2478571,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T07:10:05.000Z","msg":"#九龍城裁判法院第一庭 <br />\n#嚴舜儀主任裁判官 #提堂<br />\n👤梁(23) #1120紅磡 #營救理大<br />\n<br />\n控罪：危險駕駛<br />\n被告被控於2019年11月20日，在尖沙咀不遠處的暢運道南（地圖顯示現場為理工大學香港專上學院對開）涉嫌以危險方式駕駛一輛私家車。<br />\n===============<br />\n‼️控方申請撤銷擔保‼️<br />\n<br />\n案件暫時押後處理，以待辯方索取指示。<br />\n<br />\n#九龍城裁判法院第一庭 <br />\n#嚴舜儀主任裁判官 #提堂 <br />\n👤陳(32) #1118紅磡 #營救理大<br />\n<br />\n控罪：危險駕駛<br />\n被告被控於2019年11月18日，在紅磡繞道近理工大學李兆基樓涉嫌以危險方式駕駛一輛客貨車。<br />\n================<br />\n‼️控方申請撤銷擔保‼️<br />\n<br />\n案件暫時押後處理，以待辯方索取指示。"},{"pid":"be49be251d5496cbc8fc833db7bc672d66f5f92b","tid":2478571,"uid":87985,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T07:10:55.000Z","msg":"真係搞家長車<br />\n難怪又係張肥仔"},{"pid":"0934937c7b8c78a1333b54d1f4d79e1524e14265","tid":2478571,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be49be251d5496cbc8fc833db7bc672d66f5f92b","tid":2478571,"uid":87985,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T07:10:55.000Z","msg":"真係搞家長車<br />\n難怪又係張肥仔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T07:12:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94a4118c98a61ba473912fb776cf08c8f500dfa2","tid":2478571,"uid":14678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T07:13:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54f22770989c87d2d51327cd080e06df182839d4","tid":247857